<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI 실시간 틀린 그림 찾기 게임</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        /* 이미지 위 클릭 마커 스타일 */
        .click-marker {
            position: absolute;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border: 3px solid #ef4444;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            animation: pulse 1s infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1); border-color: #f97316; }
            100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-3 sm:p-6 text-slate-800">

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <header class="text-center my-6 sm:my-8 animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
            <span class="bg-indigo-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider shadow">AI Student Project</span>
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black mt-2 text-indigo-900 tracking-tight">🤖 AI 생성 틀린 그림 찾기</h1>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 mt-2">AI가 실시간으로 생성한 두 이미지에서 서로 다른 곳 3군데를 찾아보세요!</p>
        </header>

        <div id="progressBarContainer" class="hidden mb-6 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <span id="gameStatusBadge" class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded">게임 진행 중</span>
                <span id="roundBadge" class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded">1 / 3 라운드</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-indigo-600" id="roundStatusText">남은 틀린 그림: 3개</div>
        </div>

        <section id="setupContainer" class="max-w-xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 mb-6 animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-indigo-950">
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg
